WEBVTT

﻿1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:21.938 --> 00:00:26.651
I.O.C. Event Presentation Shanghai. China

3
00:00:41.749 --> 00:00:44.168
Wushu. the Chinese form of martial art.

4
00:00:44.418 --> 00:00:46.462
should be an Olympic event.

5
00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:49.048
It isn't about killing and vengeance.

6
00:00:49.048 --> 00:00:50.591
hatred and anger.

7
00:00:50.841 --> 00:00:52.009
Then what is Wushu?

8
00:00:52.009 --> 00:00:55.680
In Chinese. Wushu means "The Way of Combat."

9
00:00:58.474 --> 00:01:01.018
Avert. Conflict.

10
00:01:01.852 --> 00:01:06.023
The true definition of Wushu
is the way to avert conflict.

11
00:01:06.023 --> 00:01:07.108
It's about continually

12
00:01:07.358 --> 00:01:09.026
seeking to better oneself.

13
00:01:09.026 --> 00:01:11.237
Still. it begs the question. why?

14
00:01:11.487 --> 00:01:12.405
Why allow Wushu

15
00:01:12.655 --> 00:01:14.073
as an Olympic event?

16
00:01:14.615 --> 00:01:17.535
The Olympic Creed stresses
that the most important thing

17
00:01:17.785 --> 00:01:19.579
is not to win. but to take part.

18
00:01:19.829 --> 00:01:22.164
Just as the most important thing in life
is not the triumph

19
00:01:22.415 --> 00:01:23.165
but the struggle.

20
00:01:23.416 --> 00:01:27.712
You believe this ideal
embodies the spirit of Wushu?

21
00:01:28.713 --> 00:01:33.467
Yes. The answer lies over
one hundred years in the past...

22
00:01:33.718 --> 00:01:35.094
beginning with one man...

23
00:01:43.686 --> 00:01:50.443
Come here.

24
00:01:56.240 --> 00:02:00.077
Get off if you have no money.

25
00:02:12.173 --> 00:02:13.924
Set off.

26
00:03:27.540 --> 00:03:30.376
30 years ago. Huo Clan. Tianjin

27
00:04:57.838 --> 00:05:00.716
Young master. we must leave!

28
00:05:20.069 --> 00:05:21.028
Stop!

29
00:05:23.072 --> 00:05:24.281
How dare you!

30
00:05:24.532 --> 00:05:25.908
Who gave you permission to come in?

31
00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:28.285
I was bringing you tea.

32
00:05:28.285 --> 00:05:31.038
How many times have I said.
you are not allowed in here!

33
00:05:35.209 --> 00:05:36.293
Go practice your calligraphy!

34
00:05:43.384 --> 00:05:44.301
Go on!

35
00:06:03.863 --> 00:06:06.490
I do your homework everyday.

36
00:06:06.490 --> 00:06:08.909
You'd be in trouble. if your father knew.

37
00:06:15.249 --> 00:06:17.001
Don't say anything and no one will know.

38
00:06:17.251 --> 00:06:19.336
I want to show you something.

39
00:06:26.802 --> 00:06:29.179
Jinsun! Come on!

40
00:06:29.471 --> 00:06:31.223
I'm coming!

41
00:06:33.142 --> 00:06:34.894
- Come on! - I'm coming!

42
00:06:39.356 --> 00:06:40.900
I'm coming!

43
00:06:53.829 --> 00:06:55.372
Why do you take me here?

44
00:06:55.372 --> 00:06:56.790
No one of other clan is allowed here.

45
00:06:57.041 --> 00:06:58.375
Don't worry. I'm here.

46
00:06:59.835 --> 00:07:00.628
Follow me

47
00:07:04.632 --> 00:07:06.508
Declaration of Life and Death.

48
00:07:06.759 --> 00:07:09.929
Every time my dad wins. he gets one of these.

49
00:07:10.179 --> 00:07:12.389
You see how many dad has won!

50
00:07:12.765 --> 00:07:15.726
But your dad is not number one in Tianjin.

51
00:07:15.976 --> 00:07:18.145
My father will be tomorrow.

52
00:07:18.395 --> 00:07:18.854
Why?

53
00:07:19.104 --> 00:07:21.398
Don't ask. You come with me tomorrow

54
00:07:31.283 --> 00:07:32.409
Today's match is between...

55
00:07:33.202 --> 00:07:36.705
Huo Engdi of the Huo Clan...

56
00:07:37.331 --> 00:07:39.917
and Zhao Zhongqiang...

57
00:07:40.376 --> 00:07:44.129
of the Zhao Clan.

58
00:07:51.762 --> 00:07:53.973
Why are you two here? Looking for trouble?

59
00:07:54.223 --> 00:07:55.599
Your father will lose today.

60
00:07:55.849 --> 00:07:58.560
Our Huo Wushu will beat your Zhao Wushu.

61
00:07:58.560 --> 00:07:59.645
You wait and see.

62
00:08:00.521 --> 00:08:03.023
My dad will let your dad
have a taste of Zhao's blow.

63
00:08:03.273 --> 00:08:05.567
The Death Waiver has been signed.

64
00:08:06.986 --> 00:08:08.445
Win or lose. it's up to you.

65
00:08:09.113 --> 00:08:11.031
Live or die. it's up to god.

66
00:08:11.573 --> 00:08:15.828
Gentlemen. let the contest... begin!

67
00:08:39.226 --> 00:08:40.853
Zhaojian. now your father has tasted...

68
00:08:41.103 --> 00:08:42.688
the Huo Wushu!

69
00:09:15.512 --> 00:09:17.514
The winner is...

70
00:09:17.514 --> 00:09:21.518
- Zhao Zhongqiang! - Thank you!

71
00:09:31.153 --> 00:09:34.531
Yuanjia...

72
00:09:35.532 --> 00:09:45.334
Yuanjia...

73
00:09:51.423 --> 00:09:52.674
Yuanjia. let's go home.

74
00:09:53.759 --> 00:09:57.554
Yuanjia. let's go home.

75
00:09:57.888 --> 00:10:00.140
Look who's here?

76
00:10:00.474 --> 00:10:01.600
Has the cat got your tongue?

77
00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:04.311
Act like a man. Don't be a wuss.

78
00:10:04.561 --> 00:10:05.562
Get up!

79
00:10:05.562 --> 00:10:07.189
Zhao. you've gone too far!

80
00:10:07.564 --> 00:10:08.607
You shut up!

81
00:10:09.942 --> 00:10:13.237
You're worthless.
Your Huo Wushu is more worthless.

82
00:10:13.487 --> 00:10:14.863
Fight me if you dare.

83
00:10:15.155 --> 00:10:17.491
Then you'll know the Zhao Wushu...

84
00:10:21.286 --> 00:10:22.246
Get up there!

85
00:10:38.011 --> 00:10:39.555
Yuanjia. stop!

86
00:10:43.225 --> 00:10:44.143
Stop!

87
00:10:57.614 --> 00:10:59.867
Now that you've tasted my Wushu

88
00:11:00.117 --> 00:11:02.202
you can shut up about yours.

89
00:11:02.619 --> 00:11:05.664
I won. I won!

90
00:11:06.957 --> 00:11:09.209
Yuanjia. Get up. Yuanjia.

91
00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:14.548
Yuanjia. let's get out of here.

92
00:11:16.216 --> 00:11:17.217
I. Huo Yuanjia...

93
00:11:17.509 --> 00:11:19.219
swear never to be...

94
00:11:19.469 --> 00:11:20.637
defeated again!

95
00:11:21.638 --> 00:11:25.017
Jinsun. if you are my friend. please help me.

96
00:11:27.477 --> 00:11:29.438
Hurry up. hurry!

97
00:11:33.901 --> 00:11:34.943
How much longer it is going to take you?

98
00:11:39.615 --> 00:11:40.240
Look!

99
00:11:46.330 --> 00:11:47.039
Get out of here!

100
00:11:47.331 --> 00:11:48.123
Please help me copy it.

101
00:11:48.373 --> 00:11:49.541
Let's go.

102
00:11:50.500 --> 00:11:52.711
Oh. yes. you copy it here

103
00:11:52.711 --> 00:11:54.087
and take the copy home when you finish.

104
00:11:54.338 --> 00:11:55.172
My dad will beat me

105
00:11:55.422 --> 00:11:57.925
if he sees it.

106
00:12:01.261 --> 00:12:03.180
- Come back as soon as you can! - I will!

107
00:12:04.765 --> 00:12:06.683
Be very careful when you copy the last page

108
00:12:06.683 --> 00:12:08.852
on the Exterminating Blow. would you?

109
00:12:13.440 --> 00:12:15.525
Young master. why are you in the master's library?

110
00:12:16.193 --> 00:12:17.694
Are you beaten?

111
00:12:17.945 --> 00:12:21.490
Hurry. the master wants you. Come on.

112
00:12:21.865 --> 00:12:23.408
Are you ok?

113
00:12:31.250 --> 00:12:32.042
Kneel down!

114
00:12:35.587 --> 00:12:37.547
You are fighting again!

115
00:12:38.632 --> 00:12:42.010
I ask you to study.
but all you do is make trouble outside.

116
00:12:42.970 --> 00:12:43.804
Laifu.

117
00:12:45.055 --> 00:12:47.516
- bring the rod! - Yes.

118
00:12:53.397 --> 00:12:57.943
Look how he is bruised.
There is no rush to punish him.

119
00:13:00.153 --> 00:13:01.113
Master.

120
00:13:03.740 --> 00:13:04.700
- Laifu. - Yes. Madam.

121
00:13:04.950 --> 00:13:06.076
take the young master back to his room.

122
00:13:07.577 --> 00:13:10.747
Copy Confucius' The Analects ten times
and give it to me before dinner.

123
00:13:10.998 --> 00:13:12.749
- Do you understand? - Yes.

124
00:13:20.507 --> 00:13:23.760
Let me put some medicine on it.

125
00:13:25.262 --> 00:13:27.764
Lai. You may leave.

126
00:13:28.390 --> 00:13:29.182
Yes.

127
00:13:36.481 --> 00:13:38.817
Why are you upset?

128
00:13:39.067 --> 00:13:41.236
Mother. why doesn't father teach me Wushu?

129
00:13:42.779 --> 00:13:44.865
Because he cares about you.

130
00:13:45.741 --> 00:13:47.075
You have asthma.

131
00:13:47.326 --> 00:13:49.786
The training is too much for you.

132
00:13:50.078 --> 00:13:52.289
But it can make me strong.

133
00:13:54.124 --> 00:13:57.419
You want to learn just to be strong?

134
00:13:58.170 --> 00:13:59.880
When I'm good enough. I'll take revenge.

135
00:13:59.880 --> 00:14:02.591
I want Zhao to fear our Huo Wushu.

136
00:14:08.764 --> 00:14:09.765
My child.

137
00:14:10.640 --> 00:14:14.311
Wu Shu is not about winning.

138
00:14:14.728 --> 00:14:17.230
It's about discipline and self-restraint.

139
00:14:17.731 --> 00:14:21.610
One practices Wushu...

140
00:14:22.235 --> 00:14:24.821
for...

141
00:14:24.821 --> 00:14:26.073
inner strength...

142
00:14:26.490 --> 00:14:27.991
and to help...

143
00:14:27.991 --> 00:14:30.160
the weak.

144
00:14:31.828 --> 00:14:33.663
Wushu...

145
00:14:33.914 --> 00:14:37.459
is not for revenge.

146
00:14:37.751 --> 00:14:39.961
Respect must be earned.

147
00:14:39.961 --> 00:14:42.255
If I'm really good. everyone will fear me.

148
00:14:43.715 --> 00:14:44.841
Fear and respect...

149
00:14:44.841 --> 00:14:47.761
are not the same.

150
00:14:49.679 --> 00:14:52.557
Now do your penance.

151
00:14:52.849 --> 00:14:54.810
Don't make your father angry.

152
00:15:13.245 --> 00:15:14.621
Have you finished your calligraphy?

153
00:15:14.871 --> 00:15:15.872
Soon.

154
00:15:16.373 --> 00:15:18.250
- How come you do it so slow? - Don't bother.

155
00:15:18.500 --> 00:15:19.459
I'm not going to do it if you keep bothering me.

156
00:15:19.709 --> 00:15:22.295
Ok. I'm going to bother you. Hurry up.

157
00:16:10.927 --> 00:16:11.928
You dare to sign?

158
00:16:12.929 --> 00:16:14.931
Thank you for preparing all this.

159
00:16:14.931 --> 00:16:16.433
This is also what I want to do.

160
00:16:16.683 --> 00:16:17.559
After you. sir!

161
00:16:36.620 --> 00:16:38.538
You win...

162
00:16:40.749 --> 00:16:41.333
Now you have your revenge

163
00:16:41.583 --> 00:16:43.627
and can study well. right?

164
00:16:49.591 --> 00:16:50.967
Your Zhao's kung fu is nothing
but bungling oafishness.

165
00:16:50.967 --> 00:16:54.137
Today you have a taste of our Huo's kung fu.

166
00:16:54.137 --> 00:16:56.973
Remember. never brag about Zhao's kung fu again.

167
00:16:59.351 --> 00:17:00.602
Let me help you. Zhaojian.

168
00:17:00.852 --> 00:17:01.978
Get away!

169
00:17:01.978 --> 00:17:08.568
I won!

170
00:17:17.994 --> 00:17:19.996
I won!

171
00:17:19.996 --> 00:17:21.915
Fly... fly... fly...

172
00:17:22.999 --> 00:17:25.710
- You're falling down. falling...
- I'm not falling.

173
00:17:26.002 --> 00:17:29.256
- You're falling down. falling...
- I'm not falling.

174
00:17:29.506 --> 00:17:31.007
Then father knocks you down...

175
00:17:32.759 --> 00:17:37.556
I'm not falling down.

176
00:17:46.523 --> 00:17:47.857
Be careful with her.

177
00:17:52.612 --> 00:17:53.613
Good morning. Mother.

178
00:17:55.490 --> 00:17:58.910
You didn't take your medicine again.

179
00:17:59.160 --> 00:18:02.038
Mother. since I began training.

180
00:18:02.038 --> 00:18:04.040
my asthma has gone.

181
00:18:06.626 --> 00:18:08.044
Look at your daughter.

182
00:18:08.044 --> 00:18:11.256
You've spoiled her since her mother died.

183
00:18:12.048 --> 00:18:14.175
Your daughter needs a mother.

184
00:18:14.175 --> 00:18:16.970
You should marry again.

185
00:18:18.054 --> 00:18:22.142
Mother. I'm too busy building up
the family reputation.

186
00:18:22.392 --> 00:18:25.228
Soon everyone in Tianjin
will respect the Huo name.

187
00:18:25.937 --> 00:18:27.439
There's no time for marriage.

188
00:18:29.065 --> 00:18:30.442
Father. I want to go see you fight.

189
00:18:30.692 --> 00:18:34.070
All these years. you haven't lost.

190
00:18:34.946 --> 00:18:37.699
Your most formidable enemy...

191
00:18:38.325 --> 00:18:40.160
lies...

192
00:18:40.577 --> 00:18:42.829
within you.

193
00:18:43.246 --> 00:18:44.664
Oh. I get it.

194
00:18:51.087 --> 00:18:52.088
Young master...

195
00:18:53.548 --> 00:18:54.883
Oh. yes.

196
00:18:57.510 --> 00:18:59.804
Mother. why not go take a rest?

197
00:19:06.102 --> 00:19:06.978
Father.

198
00:19:07.395 --> 00:19:09.397
your fist wasn't fast enough...

199
00:19:09.898 --> 00:19:11.232
and your heart wasn't hard enough.

200
00:19:11.650 --> 00:19:13.818
Rest assured. as long as I live.

201
00:19:14.319 --> 00:19:17.113
the Huo family will never lose again.

202
00:19:31.127 --> 00:19:33.296
I'll be the Champion of Tianjin.

203
00:19:33.630 --> 00:19:34.547
Father!

204
00:19:36.132 --> 00:19:37.133
Jade!

205
00:19:40.303 --> 00:19:42.138
- For me? - No.

206
00:19:42.138 --> 00:19:44.808
- Please! - No.

207
00:19:45.183 --> 00:19:46.601
When do I get it?

208
00:19:47.018 --> 00:19:49.145
When you win.

209
00:19:49.521 --> 00:19:50.897
- Really! - Yes.

210
00:19:51.147 --> 00:19:52.232
Promise?

211
00:19:55.902 --> 00:19:58.947
Tianjin 1900

212
00:20:06.204 --> 00:20:07.914
Master. you always win.

213
00:20:10.875 --> 00:20:14.587
Master Huo.
When you will be the Champion of the world?

214
00:20:15.171 --> 00:20:16.381
I don't know. What do you think?

215
00:20:17.173 --> 00:20:20.135
Today! It'll be today!

216
00:20:41.156 --> 00:20:42.198
Hi. Zhao!

217
00:20:42.574 --> 00:20:44.200
Where have you been hiding all these years?

218
00:20:44.492 --> 00:20:48.288
I've fought in 38 cities in 17 provinces.

219
00:20:48.288 --> 00:20:49.831
My skills are so good...

220
00:20:50.081 --> 00:20:51.583
that I remain undefeated.

221
00:20:53.209 --> 00:20:54.210
Bullshit!

222
00:20:54.210 --> 00:20:55.503
You're bullshit!

223
00:20:56.212 --> 00:20:58.214
The Death Waiver has been signed.

224
00:20:58.214 --> 00:21:01.050
Let the contest begins!

225
00:21:10.518 --> 00:21:12.228
Come! Come on up!

226
00:21:21.237 --> 00:21:24.449
What's the matter? Scared?

227
00:21:24.699 --> 00:21:26.367
Afraid you'll fall and hurt yourself?

228
00:21:26.618 --> 00:21:27.494
In your dreams!

229
00:21:39.255 --> 00:21:40.757
Great! Master!

230
00:22:46.155 --> 00:22:49.033
I am unyielding like a mountain.
My legs - the firm bedrock.

231
00:22:49.284 --> 00:22:51.327
Today. Huo Wushu becomes history.

232
00:22:51.327 --> 00:22:53.580
Fine! You'll have your chance...

233
00:22:54.080 --> 00:22:54.914
to lose!

234
00:23:26.738 --> 00:23:28.573
- Cat's paw? - Tiger's claw!

235
00:23:45.924 --> 00:23:46.674
Give up!

236
00:23:52.221 --> 00:23:53.514
Great!

237
00:23:55.308 --> 00:23:56.392
You think you'd win so easily?

238
00:23:56.726 --> 00:23:58.770
- Cat's paw! - Tiger's claw!

239
00:24:18.665 --> 00:24:19.707
You've lost!

240
00:24:30.969 --> 00:24:32.095
Be careful!

241
00:24:40.395 --> 00:24:41.437
Master!

242
00:24:42.146 --> 00:24:43.731
- Are you OK? - I'm fine!

243
00:24:44.649 --> 00:24:46.067
So. you're still alive!

244
00:24:49.946 --> 00:24:51.114
- Don't touch me! - Master!

245
00:24:51.364 --> 00:24:52.448
The winner is...

246
00:24:52.448 --> 00:24:53.700
Huo Yuanjia!

247
00:24:56.369 --> 00:24:59.998
Thank you. Thank you.

248
00:25:02.542 --> 00:25:03.751
Thank you. Thank you.

249
00:25:31.446 --> 00:25:32.488
Master.

250
00:25:32.739 --> 00:25:34.490
Thank you.

251
00:25:34.490 --> 00:25:37.160
Congratulations!

252
00:25:37.493 --> 00:25:38.703
Thank you.

253
00:25:40.413 --> 00:25:41.581
This way please. Master Huo.

254
00:25:41.831 --> 00:25:43.124
Thank you.

255
00:25:43.374 --> 00:25:45.501
- Yuanjia! - Hey. Jinsun!

256
00:25:47.754 --> 00:25:48.921
You've just arrived?

257
00:25:49.505 --> 00:25:50.590
Your usual table is ready.

258
00:25:51.799 --> 00:25:58.014
Congratulations!

259
00:25:58.765 --> 00:26:01.517
Thanks. thanks.

260
00:26:02.518 --> 00:26:04.062
Come on! Drink up!

261
00:26:07.356 --> 00:26:09.358
Jinsun. your restaurant is...

262
00:26:09.609 --> 00:26:11.194
more popular than ever.

263
00:26:11.444 --> 00:26:13.946
Thanks to all my friends. it's getting by.

264
00:26:14.530 --> 00:26:15.573
When we were young...

265
00:26:16.407 --> 00:26:17.784
you were such a nerd!

266
00:26:18.034 --> 00:26:20.536
Who could imagine you'd become
such a great business man?

267
00:26:20.536 --> 00:26:23.748
No one will pay me to read books all day.

268
00:26:23.998 --> 00:26:24.624
But being a businessman?

269
00:26:24.874 --> 00:26:26.542
It's a living.

270
00:26:27.794 --> 00:26:29.629
Yuanjia. you must try these.

271
00:26:29.879 --> 00:26:32.882
I've recruited the best chefs...
from across the country.

272
00:26:33.132 --> 00:26:34.592
Have a taste. Tell me what you think.

273
00:26:34.842 --> 00:26:36.552
Come. come. eat!

274
00:26:36.844 --> 00:26:39.055
Master. after you.

275
00:26:44.352 --> 00:26:46.187
- I'm Xia Xiang. - I'm Xu DaShan.

276
00:26:46.479 --> 00:26:48.815
Please take us as your disciples
We want to learn Huo Wushu...

277
00:26:49.065 --> 00:26:51.109
and we'll devote ourselves to you!

278
00:26:52.151 --> 00:26:54.237
Good! You look tough enough.

279
00:26:54.529 --> 00:26:55.488
Give them drinks!

280
00:26:57.573 --> 00:26:59.575
Bottoms up and we'll all be brothers.

281
00:26:59.575 --> 00:27:00.576
Cheers!

282
00:27:01.577 --> 00:27:03.579
Master Huo. congratulations!

283
00:27:03.579 --> 00:27:04.580
Thanks. master.

284
00:27:07.416 --> 00:27:08.584
Today is a joyous occasion.

285
00:27:08.584 --> 00:27:10.586
Everything's on me!

286
00:27:11.963 --> 00:27:12.880
Enjoy!

287
00:27:13.422 --> 00:27:14.841
Have a seat!

288
00:27:15.591 --> 00:27:17.677
Come. come. eat!

289
00:27:21.430 --> 00:27:22.557
Jade!

290
00:27:22.932 --> 00:27:25.893
It's time for bed.

291
00:27:26.144 --> 00:27:28.354
Go tuck her in.

292
00:27:33.359 --> 00:27:35.611
Miss. it's time for bed.

293
00:27:35.611 --> 00:27:37.572
Be a good girl. come on.

294
00:27:37.822 --> 00:27:40.658
It's bed time. Come on...

295
00:27:58.259 --> 00:27:59.635
What's this? It tastes horrible!

296
00:27:59.969 --> 00:28:01.637
It's called "Coffee."

297
00:28:01.637 --> 00:28:03.890
A western thing. Not used to it. are you?

298
00:28:04.640 --> 00:28:07.310
These are turbulent times.

299
00:28:07.643 --> 00:28:08.936
Our country has grown weak.

300
00:28:09.187 --> 00:28:11.647
The West is dominating us.

301
00:28:12.148 --> 00:28:13.649
People like me must not...

302
00:28:13.649 --> 00:28:15.109
be concerned only with money.

303
00:28:15.651 --> 00:28:16.777
People like you should not...

304
00:28:17.195 --> 00:28:19.155
be concerned only with fighting.

305
00:28:19.447 --> 00:28:20.781
Our country deserves better.

306
00:28:21.532 --> 00:28:24.619
Politics is for intellectuals.

307
00:28:25.036 --> 00:28:27.663
I'm just a fighter. To be the Champion
of Tianjin is all I care about.

308
00:28:28.289 --> 00:28:30.541
It's that important to you?

309
00:28:32.335 --> 00:28:34.670
Come. let me show you something.

310
00:28:35.129 --> 00:28:36.172
Jinsun.

311
00:28:36.631 --> 00:28:38.841
you've only... watched a fight from below.

312
00:28:39.091 --> 00:28:42.011
Now you're standing up right here.
Do you feel the difference?

313
00:28:42.970 --> 00:28:44.347
What difference?

314
00:28:47.225 --> 00:28:48.684
When you are down there...

315
00:28:49.560 --> 00:28:51.520
life and death up here has nothing to do with you.

316
00:28:51.979 --> 00:28:53.689
It's all entertainment.

317
00:28:54.232 --> 00:28:55.650
But when you are up here...

318
00:28:55.900 --> 00:28:57.818
you must not lose. You have to win!

319
00:28:58.653 --> 00:29:00.696
But you can choose not to be here.

320
00:29:04.742 --> 00:29:06.285
Jinsun. listen!

321
00:29:09.705 --> 00:29:10.706
To what?

322
00:29:11.707 --> 00:29:13.251
I don't hear anything.

323
00:29:17.713 --> 00:29:19.131
I can hear you...

324
00:29:20.216 --> 00:29:22.426
Master Huo. you're our hero!

325
00:29:25.012 --> 00:29:28.724
Great! That's great!

326
00:29:28.975 --> 00:29:30.726
Master is the champion of the world.

327
00:29:56.711 --> 00:29:58.421
Iron head kungfu!

328
00:30:26.574 --> 00:30:27.575
Thanks a lot.

329
00:30:29.410 --> 00:30:31.829
That's great!

330
00:30:32.163 --> 00:30:33.539
Hey! This is taking too long.

331
00:30:33.789 --> 00:30:36.167
Get everyone who has signed a waiver
to come up all at once.

332
00:30:36.917 --> 00:30:38.794
All you challengers.

333
00:30:38.794 --> 00:30:40.087
get up there!

334
00:31:31.430 --> 00:31:32.431
Huo Yuanjia.

335
00:31:32.681 --> 00:31:35.017
when will you be the Champion of Tianjin?

336
00:31:35.267 --> 00:31:36.435
What do you think?

337
00:31:36.977 --> 00:31:39.939
Today! It'll be today!

338
00:31:57.248 --> 00:31:58.916
Let's eat.

339
00:31:59.375 --> 00:32:00.126
Yes. Madam.

340
00:32:02.420 --> 00:32:03.462
You must be hungry.

341
00:32:04.880 --> 00:32:08.008
Here. eat some of this.

342
00:32:16.725 --> 00:32:19.645
What's the matter?

343
00:32:22.565 --> 00:32:25.276
We seek to be your disciples...

344
00:32:25.526 --> 00:32:26.819
and devote ourselves to you.

345
00:32:27.903 --> 00:32:29.947
Fine! You may join.

346
00:32:29.947 --> 00:32:31.282
Come on. Give them drinks! A round for everyone.

347
00:32:36.829 --> 00:32:39.790
Bottoms up and we'll all be brothers!

348
00:32:40.291 --> 00:32:42.001
Come on. come on.

349
00:32:42.460 --> 00:32:44.003
- Come on. come on. - Master Huo...

350
00:32:44.253 --> 00:32:47.047
Master Huo. congratulations!
You're the true Champion of Tianjin!

351
00:32:49.717 --> 00:32:51.051
See you. Have a good day.

352
00:32:51.051 --> 00:32:54.638
Come on. you're not drinking?

353
00:32:55.222 --> 00:32:57.933
Master Huo's bills are long overdue.

354
00:33:00.603 --> 00:33:01.770
Alright. Alright.

355
00:33:03.856 --> 00:33:06.108
A toast!

356
00:33:10.237 --> 00:33:10.988
Bring a bigger jug!

357
00:33:11.238 --> 00:33:13.073
Hey. you're not drinking?
Now you must drink two more!

358
00:33:13.741 --> 00:33:15.743
You have not fought my godfather Master Chin.

359
00:33:20.039 --> 00:33:21.540
Come on...

360
00:33:22.583 --> 00:33:23.250
Yuanjia...

361
00:33:23.501 --> 00:33:25.085
You've won 38 contests in a row.

362
00:33:25.336 --> 00:33:26.629
and defeated every fighter in Tianjin.

363
00:33:26.879 --> 00:33:28.422
There's no one left.

364
00:33:31.091 --> 00:33:32.259
No. you're wrong.

365
00:33:33.302 --> 00:33:34.637
There is still one left to beat.

366
00:33:36.180 --> 00:33:37.973
So you are not going to stop?

367
00:33:41.977 --> 00:33:45.022
I want to be the true Champion of Tianjin.
I must fight.

368
00:33:46.148 --> 00:33:47.733
What about elsewhere?

369
00:33:48.025 --> 00:33:51.153
Beijing. Guangdong. Hunan?

370
00:33:51.987 --> 00:33:54.031
When will you stop?

371
00:33:55.658 --> 00:33:58.244
I know what you're saying.

372
00:33:58.744 --> 00:33:59.745
But I cannot stop now.

373
00:33:59.995 --> 00:34:01.038
I need to prove that

374
00:34:01.705 --> 00:34:04.083
I am the best... the strongest.

375
00:34:04.333 --> 00:34:07.169
For what? You will always be you.

376
00:34:07.419 --> 00:34:09.255
You'll never become someone else!

377
00:34:09.713 --> 00:34:11.006
Yuanjia

378
00:34:11.006 --> 00:34:14.176
I think you should take a break and reconsider.

379
00:34:14.176 --> 00:34:15.261
What's this?

380
00:34:18.681 --> 00:34:21.058
These...

381
00:34:21.058 --> 00:34:22.935
are your bills.

382
00:34:24.228 --> 00:34:25.521
I'll take care of it.

383
00:34:27.022 --> 00:34:29.441
All your so-called disciples. only come

384
00:34:29.984 --> 00:34:32.027
for the free drinks and food.

385
00:34:32.611 --> 00:34:35.072
You don't understand our circle.

386
00:34:35.322 --> 00:34:36.824
Our circle...

387
00:34:38.200 --> 00:34:39.410
Fine.

388
00:34:39.743 --> 00:34:42.037
I will settle the bills tomorrow.

389
00:34:42.871 --> 00:34:44.081
Yuanjia.

390
00:34:44.081 --> 00:34:46.041
I am not here for your money

391
00:34:46.417 --> 00:34:48.294
I only want to remind you

392
00:34:48.794 --> 00:34:50.296
Please be careful with the people...

393
00:34:50.546 --> 00:34:53.173
in your inner circle.

394
00:34:53.716 --> 00:34:55.801
Judge them by their integrity. not their drinking.

395
00:35:11.775 --> 00:35:12.484
Good morning.

396
00:35:12.735 --> 00:35:14.194
Good morning. Master Huo!

397
00:35:14.194 --> 00:35:16.697
Good morning. Master Huo!

398
00:35:16.947 --> 00:35:19.992
- Good morning. Master Chin! - Good morning

399
00:35:28.542 --> 00:35:30.044
What a coincidence

400
00:35:30.294 --> 00:35:32.212
to run into the...

401
00:35:32.588 --> 00:35:34.089
self-proclaimed Champion of Tianjin!

402
00:35:34.089 --> 00:35:36.884
Master Chin. it's been a long time.

403
00:35:37.343 --> 00:35:39.345
At your age...

404
00:35:39.595 --> 00:35:41.013
I thought you'd retired.

405
00:35:41.639 --> 00:35:44.516
Too many disciples.

406
00:35:44.767 --> 00:35:47.269
I cannot retire even if I wanted to.

407
00:35:47.269 --> 00:35:49.730
Oh! Is that so?

408
00:35:50.147 --> 00:35:52.107
Then this big coffin is a gift to yourself?

409
00:35:52.107 --> 00:35:53.108
Enjoy it soon!

410
00:35:55.277 --> 00:35:56.320
You're too kind.

411
00:35:57.780 --> 00:36:00.991
Actually. this is my gift to you!

412
00:36:03.994 --> 00:36:07.122
Your master needs help!.

413
00:36:09.291 --> 00:36:11.752
Master Chin. this way please!

414
00:36:29.144 --> 00:36:30.145
Stop!

415
00:36:32.147 --> 00:36:35.192
If you want to learn Wushu.
you need to work hard at it.

416
00:36:37.695 --> 00:36:40.406
Work hard?

417
00:36:43.826 --> 00:36:47.955
The perfecting of skills
needs time and determination.

418
00:36:48.664 --> 00:36:50.207
Tell me... Stand off!

419
00:36:50.207 --> 00:36:51.166
Stand off!

420
00:36:51.166 --> 00:36:52.167
Stand off!

421
00:36:53.794 --> 00:36:56.004
Give it two or three years. and you will
only have some superficial knowledge.

422
00:37:00.134 --> 00:37:01.719
Well. this is twenty year's practice.

423
00:37:02.010 --> 00:37:03.262
Can you handle this?

424
00:37:04.179 --> 00:37:05.180
Go on!

425
00:37:10.686 --> 00:37:11.770
Young master.

426
00:37:12.187 --> 00:37:13.814
the income of the Wushu school...

427
00:37:14.064 --> 00:37:15.691
barely covers the household overhead.

428
00:37:16.108 --> 00:37:18.861
Your disciples have incurred

429
00:37:19.111 --> 00:37:20.612
a large expense.

430
00:37:23.365 --> 00:37:24.867
What about the household reserve?

431
00:37:25.200 --> 00:37:28.287
It's been depleted three months ago.

432
00:37:29.037 --> 00:37:32.207
Depleted? Depleted.

433
00:37:34.293 --> 00:37:36.712
Master! Master!

434
00:37:39.047 --> 00:37:41.800
How many times have I told you
to hone your skills.

435
00:37:42.050 --> 00:37:43.051
No one listens.

436
00:37:45.220 --> 00:37:46.346
Who did this?

437
00:37:47.514 --> 00:37:48.766
Master Chin!

438
00:37:53.729 --> 00:37:55.022
Master.

439
00:38:02.821 --> 00:38:03.989
Master.

440
00:38:09.036 --> 00:38:14.333
We celebrate Master Chin's birthday.

441
00:38:14.583 --> 00:38:18.378
Wishing him good fortune.

442
00:38:18.378 --> 00:38:19.379
Terrific!

443
00:38:21.131 --> 00:38:21.965
Godfather!

444
00:38:22.382 --> 00:38:24.426
We wish you good fortune...

445
00:38:24.760 --> 00:38:26.261
and great health.

446
00:38:37.272 --> 00:38:40.275
Wish you a prolong life.

447
00:38:40.275 --> 00:38:41.693
Great! Great!

448
00:38:46.949 --> 00:38:47.741
Master Huo.

449
00:38:48.283 --> 00:38:49.785
today's my godfather's birthday.

450
00:38:50.285 --> 00:38:51.578
These tables are reserved.

451
00:38:52.287 --> 00:38:54.790
As a favour to me. please drink somewhere else.

452
00:38:56.583 --> 00:38:57.751
Master Huo. please do me a favour...

453
00:38:59.586 --> 00:39:00.963
You don't qualify to speak to me.

454
00:39:05.217 --> 00:39:06.260
Hey!

455
00:39:06.677 --> 00:39:08.512
I'm not in the mood to fight...

456
00:39:08.971 --> 00:39:10.472
on my birthday.

457
00:39:10.472 --> 00:39:13.183
Maybe some other time.

458
00:39:16.603 --> 00:39:19.398
You injured my disciple.

459
00:39:19.731 --> 00:39:21.275
You should be ashamed of yourself.

460
00:39:21.525 --> 00:39:24.319
I'm here to settle the score.

461
00:39:25.612 --> 00:39:26.905
What do you want?

462
00:39:29.700 --> 00:39:32.369
It's signed. Do you have the guts to sign it too?

463
00:39:32.369 --> 00:39:35.330
Otherwise. get on your knees and apologise.

464
00:39:36.915 --> 00:39:38.417
Yuanjia!

465
00:39:41.044 --> 00:39:42.045
You've crossed the line. Don't be...

466
00:39:42.296 --> 00:39:42.921
so rude in front of his guests.

467
00:39:43.171 --> 00:39:45.424
If you've got a problem. let's talk tomorrow.

468
00:39:45.424 --> 00:39:48.343
My disciple's hurt. I must do something.

469
00:39:48.927 --> 00:39:49.970
I don't care what happened.

470
00:39:50.220 --> 00:39:53.015
But you mustn't spoil their celebration.

471
00:39:56.768 --> 00:39:58.437
I'm not here to spoil anything.

472
00:39:58.437 --> 00:39:59.354
Yuanjia!

473
00:39:59.354 --> 00:40:01.356
You think I might trash your place.

474
00:40:01.356 --> 00:40:03.817
I'll pay all damages to the last penny!

475
00:40:08.488 --> 00:40:11.825
How can you talk like this?

476
00:40:13.035 --> 00:40:14.369
You should go.

477
00:40:14.369 --> 00:40:16.872
Forget that we've ever been friends!

478
00:40:19.541 --> 00:40:21.376
You're asking me to leave?

479
00:40:23.754 --> 00:40:25.380
You're willing to throw away...

480
00:40:26.381 --> 00:40:28.050
our friendship?

481
00:40:30.218 --> 00:40:31.803
Everybody out!

482
00:40:32.804 --> 00:40:34.598
My sword seeks vengeance!

483
00:40:38.143 --> 00:40:39.603
Stay at your own peril!

484
00:45:38.693 --> 00:45:39.819
Master! Master!

485
00:45:40.070 --> 00:45:43.740
The Master has won!

486
00:45:43.990 --> 00:45:47.535
Let's drink!

487
00:47:08.783 --> 00:47:09.951
Master Huo.

488
00:47:13.038 --> 00:47:14.497
Congratulations!

489
00:47:15.415 --> 00:47:16.458
You got your wish.

490
00:47:16.708 --> 00:47:18.376
You're finally the Champion of Tianjin.

491
00:47:19.294 --> 00:47:20.795
You might like to know...

492
00:47:21.379 --> 00:47:24.507
Master Chin died two hours ago.

493
00:47:40.982 --> 00:47:42.359
Huo Yuanjia!

494
00:47:44.652 --> 00:47:47.822
When will you be the Champion?

495
00:47:50.825 --> 00:47:52.535
It'll be today!

496
00:47:52.786 --> 00:47:54.662
It'll be today!

497
00:47:55.413 --> 00:47:56.664
Huo Yuanjia!

498
00:47:56.998 --> 00:47:58.792
It'll be today!

499
00:47:59.751 --> 00:48:01.628
It'll be today!

500
00:48:02.420 --> 00:48:03.546
Huo Yuanjia!

501
00:48:03.797 --> 00:48:06.841
Champion of Tianjin! Today is the day!

502
00:50:26.981 --> 00:50:28.066
Yes. I killed your family!

503
00:50:29.234 --> 00:50:30.860
I am responsible.

504
00:50:32.654 --> 00:50:34.614
Godmother. take good care.

505
00:51:23.454 --> 00:51:26.165
Tell the Master the truth.

506
00:51:26.165 --> 00:51:27.292
Master.

507
00:51:28.042 --> 00:51:29.294
it's all my fault.

508
00:51:29.961 --> 00:51:31.129
I'm very sorry.

509
00:51:32.130 --> 00:51:33.798
I was drunk...

510
00:51:34.048 --> 00:51:37.260
I insulted Master Chin's wife.

511
00:51:38.511 --> 00:51:40.847
He was teaching me a lesson.

512
00:51:45.435 --> 00:51:48.104
All the brothers knew.

513
00:51:48.104 --> 00:51:50.773
but nobody told you.

514
00:51:51.941 --> 00:51:56.362
Master... Master!

515
00:51:57.822 --> 00:52:01.075
Master.

516
00:54:39.192 --> 00:54:44.030
Come along. Yuanjia.

517
00:54:58.294 --> 00:55:00.254
He is burning up.

518
00:55:00.755 --> 00:55:01.714
Let me make some herbal medicine.

519
00:55:01.964 --> 00:55:04.717
He'll feel better.

520
00:55:36.040 --> 00:55:39.210
Drink. my dear. You'll feel better afterwards.

521
00:56:46.569 --> 00:56:47.778
You woke up.

522
00:56:50.281 --> 00:56:51.741
I will bring you some warm congee.

523
00:57:15.389 --> 00:57:16.891
He's awake. Grandma.

524
00:57:17.141 --> 00:57:18.184
That's good.

525
00:57:25.066 --> 00:57:29.070
Leave it. He's going to sleep. Let's go

526
00:57:29.779 --> 00:57:32.740
Go.

527
00:57:32.990 --> 00:57:35.368
He's going to sleep. Go.

528
00:58:41.559 --> 00:58:42.643
It's time for lunch.

529
00:58:54.947 --> 00:58:56.490
When I was 13...

530
00:58:56.949 --> 00:58:58.617
my eyesight began to fail.

531
00:58:59.493 --> 00:59:02.496
Everything turned blurry.

532
00:59:03.289 --> 00:59:04.749
I cried a lot.

533
00:59:06.333 --> 00:59:07.501
My Grandma told me...

534
00:59:08.502 --> 00:59:11.047
cry if you are sad.

535
00:59:11.505 --> 00:59:13.591
When there are no more tears. life will go on.

536
00:59:15.843 --> 00:59:18.679
I can see everything in my heart.

537
00:59:18.679 --> 00:59:19.889
Do you believe me?

538
00:59:39.575 --> 00:59:41.327
I'll wash your hair.

539
01:00:26.539 --> 01:00:28.582
Your hair will get knotted...

540
01:00:29.291 --> 01:00:31.001
if you don't wash it often.

541
01:00:33.587 --> 01:00:37.591
Grandma always says...

542
01:00:38.342 --> 01:00:40.511
cleanliness brings purity to life.

543
01:00:41.720 --> 01:00:43.597
Every knot can be untangled.

544
01:01:00.239 --> 01:01:02.074
Huang. you've been through. It's not easy. is it?

545
01:01:02.575 --> 01:01:04.910
so many years with us.

546
01:01:06.996 --> 01:01:10.875
Grandma. Huang doesn't seem to be alright

547
01:01:12.501 --> 01:01:15.004
Everyone has this day.

548
01:01:15.629 --> 01:01:18.632
It's time for Huang to rest.

549
01:01:21.093 --> 01:01:23.971
What about him? He also needs to rest?

550
01:01:24.638 --> 01:01:28.601
He needs a long sleep.

551
01:01:28.851 --> 01:01:33.314
When he wakes up. he will know what to do.

552
01:01:37.902 --> 01:01:39.653
I found this in your clothes.

553
01:01:46.660 --> 01:01:48.662
Let's go and let Huang rest.

554
01:02:56.730 --> 01:02:57.898
Ox!

555
01:02:58.732 --> 01:03:00.067
You sleep a lot!

556
01:03:00.317 --> 01:03:02.361
You slept as much as our ox...

557
01:03:02.611 --> 01:03:04.071
that's why we call you Ox.

558
01:03:04.363 --> 01:03:06.156
Come this way.

559
01:03:12.329 --> 01:03:14.540
Ox. you've waken up?

560
01:03:16.583 --> 01:03:18.627
Let's catch some dragonflies. Let's go!

561
01:03:20.838 --> 01:03:22.881
Let's catch some dragonflies.

562
01:05:02.856 --> 01:05:04.650
Let's go. Huang.

563
01:05:10.155 --> 01:05:12.157
Huang. let's go home.

564
01:05:13.283 --> 01:05:14.576
Come on. Grandma here

565
01:05:15.869 --> 01:05:18.872
Huang. no need to come to the field today.
You can rest.

566
01:05:19.373 --> 01:05:21.875
Grandma knows you have tried your best.

567
01:05:22.584 --> 01:05:26.380
Come. come with Grandma.

568
01:05:27.881 --> 01:05:28.882
Ok.

569
01:05:32.261 --> 01:05:33.887
Huang. come with me.

570
01:05:36.807 --> 01:05:38.100
Huang is used to coming

571
01:05:38.434 --> 01:05:40.519
to the field everyday to work.

572
01:05:40.769 --> 01:05:42.020
It's so endurant and hard-working

573
01:05:44.523 --> 01:05:45.899
Now it knows that it wouldn't live very long

574
01:05:46.650 --> 01:05:49.903
and yet it still wants to help.

575
01:05:51.155 --> 01:05:52.906
It has done so much for us

576
01:05:53.782 --> 01:05:55.784
and never asked anything in return.

577
01:06:51.298 --> 01:06:55.135
Eat something. my dear.
Everything will pass. Eat something.

578
01:07:02.184 --> 01:07:06.355
The men in the city go to the exam.

579
01:07:06.980 --> 01:07:12.694
They will grow if they succeed in the exam.

580
01:07:13.237 --> 01:07:14.112
Eat something.

581
01:07:15.072 --> 01:07:16.281
Eat more.

582
01:07:19.368 --> 01:07:21.995
Tomorrow. you should take him...

583
01:07:21.995 --> 01:07:23.539
to work in the fields.

584
01:07:23.830 --> 01:07:25.749
He'll feel better.

585
01:08:22.639 --> 01:08:23.932
Ox...

586
01:08:53.545 --> 01:08:56.798
Ox... Ox... come...

587
01:08:57.174 --> 01:08:59.926
Come. quick.

588
01:09:01.595 --> 01:09:04.097
Look! Moon told me not to say anything.

589
01:09:04.097 --> 01:09:06.099
You did a bad job.

590
01:09:06.099 --> 01:09:07.934
She is re-planting for you.

591
01:09:27.371 --> 01:09:28.955
Seedlings are alive.

592
01:09:29.289 --> 01:09:31.208
If you plant them too close together...

593
01:09:31.875 --> 01:09:33.335
they will not grow.

594
01:09:34.294 --> 01:09:35.379
Just like people...

595
01:09:35.879 --> 01:09:37.756
they need to respect each other...

596
01:09:38.131 --> 01:09:40.133
in order to live together peacefully.

597
01:09:43.136 --> 01:09:44.304
I'll always remember.

598
01:10:40.861 --> 01:10:43.196
I want my Huang...

599
01:10:43.196 --> 01:10:45.699
I want my Huang.... I won't let it go.

600
01:10:45.949 --> 01:10:48.201
I want my Huang...

601
01:10:48.201 --> 01:10:51.913
I want my Huang... I won't let it go.

602
01:10:52.164 --> 01:10:56.334
Gui...

603
01:11:00.338 --> 01:11:04.968
Gui. you are too young to understand.

604
01:11:05.218 --> 01:11:07.679
Huang leaves this world in peace.

605
01:11:08.180 --> 01:11:11.183
since he had done what he needed to do.

606
01:11:11.808 --> 01:11:14.227
Everyone dies.

607
01:11:14.519 --> 01:11:16.354
So does Huang.

608
01:11:16.354 --> 01:11:20.317
but one only leaves in peace

609
01:11:20.609 --> 01:11:23.987
when there is no regret in one's life.

610
01:11:24.237 --> 01:11:26.615
Don't cry. my boy.

611
01:12:03.235 --> 01:12:06.238
Gui has a problem!

612
01:12:08.281 --> 01:12:09.491
What happened to him?

613
01:12:10.742 --> 01:12:11.952
He missed his bull so much

614
01:12:12.202 --> 01:12:14.287
that he stole one from the Siam clan.

615
01:12:14.538 --> 01:12:15.914
He got caught over there

616
01:12:17.415 --> 01:12:20.585
and they are about to punish him
according to their law.

617
01:12:20.836 --> 01:12:25.298
Let's go to save Gui!

618
01:12:35.308 --> 01:12:38.019
Help me...

619
01:12:39.563 --> 01:12:40.480
Help me...

620
01:12:40.480 --> 01:12:41.606
Beat him.

621
01:12:46.486 --> 01:12:48.405
Help me...

622
01:12:49.948 --> 01:12:51.449
help me...

623
01:12:53.869 --> 01:12:56.204
Help me...

624
01:12:56.955 --> 01:12:59.332
Are you coming for a fight?

625
01:12:59.332 --> 01:13:03.003
Gui made a mistake and should be punished.

626
01:13:03.336 --> 01:13:05.505
You have already punished him enough.

627
01:13:05.755 --> 01:13:10.510
I'm here to make a formal apology.

628
01:13:12.762 --> 01:13:15.432
The boy doesn't know any better.

629
01:13:15.432 --> 01:13:18.435
Let us take him back.

630
01:13:18.435 --> 01:13:22.522
Indeed he is a child.

631
01:13:22.522 --> 01:13:23.815
But even for children in our village.

632
01:13:24.065 --> 01:13:27.319
we beat them for the burning time of an incense

633
01:13:28.236 --> 01:13:30.739
so they will remember the lesson.

634
01:13:30.989 --> 01:13:32.157
Go on. Beat him.

635
01:13:36.703 --> 01:13:37.746
Help me!

636
01:13:37.996 --> 01:13:40.707
The child can't take it.
Let me take the beating for him!

637
01:13:42.250 --> 01:13:43.376
Stop!

638
01:13:53.803 --> 01:13:55.388
Let me take the beatings for Gui.

639
01:13:57.849 --> 01:13:59.476
Well. this punishment is for children.

640
01:14:05.941 --> 01:14:09.361
Adults should be punished in another way.

641
01:14:09.611 --> 01:14:10.946
How?

642
01:14:14.991 --> 01:14:17.285
Take on my iron fist.

643
01:14:22.415 --> 01:14:24.125
If I am still standing
when this incense burns out.

644
01:14:24.376 --> 01:14:27.003
you will have to release the child.

645
01:14:29.756 --> 01:14:32.926
Sure! No argument about life and death?

646
01:14:35.553 --> 01:14:36.846
No argument!

647
01:14:38.431 --> 01:14:39.891
It's settled then?

648
01:14:40.433 --> 01:14:41.685
Yes.

649
01:15:03.456 --> 01:15:05.458
Grandma. what's wrong with him?

650
01:15:33.028 --> 01:15:35.739
Ox. Ox!

651
01:15:38.491 --> 01:15:40.493
You don't want to hurt others.

652
01:15:41.161 --> 01:15:43.496
but you should let others hurt you.

653
01:15:43.747 --> 01:15:44.998
son!

654
01:15:47.500 --> 01:15:50.503
How can we stand this! Let's help him.

655
01:15:51.838 --> 01:15:52.964
Stop!

656
01:15:53.381 --> 01:15:54.424
Stop!

657
01:15:59.220 --> 01:16:00.513
The incense is still burning.

658
01:16:32.420 --> 01:16:36.174
Stand up. stand up...

659
01:16:36.424 --> 01:16:38.676
Keep beating... beat him.

660
01:16:38.676 --> 01:16:42.555
The incense has burnt out. You lose. you lose...

661
01:16:48.394 --> 01:16:49.437
Let him go!

662
01:16:53.024 --> 01:16:54.901
Let's go home. Gui. Go.

663
01:17:37.610 --> 01:17:39.737
Time to go home.

664
01:17:39.988 --> 01:17:43.032
I want to stay a little longer with Ox.

665
01:17:43.283 --> 01:17:43.992
I don't go home.

666
01:17:44.242 --> 01:17:45.618
Gui. aren't you hungry?

667
01:17:45.618 --> 01:17:47.162
Are you not hungry? Ox might be hungry.

668
01:17:47.620 --> 01:17:48.580
No. I am not hungry.

669
01:17:48.830 --> 01:17:50.206
I can stay here a little longer with Gui.

670
01:17:51.624 --> 01:17:52.709
Ox. you are the best.

671
01:17:53.209 --> 01:17:55.044
So what does that make me?

672
01:17:57.755 --> 01:17:59.382
Aunt Moon.

673
01:17:59.632 --> 01:18:02.635
can you ask Ox a favour for me?

674
01:18:02.969 --> 01:18:04.220
You and Ox are so close.

675
01:18:04.470 --> 01:18:05.763
why do you need my help?

676
01:18:05.763 --> 01:18:08.641
Because. you are the dearest to Ox.

677
01:18:10.560 --> 01:18:13.980
Don't talk nonsense.

678
01:18:14.981 --> 01:18:18.318
Gui. you can ask me yourself.

679
01:18:18.776 --> 01:18:20.695
You keep refusing to teach me martial arts.
but I really want to learn.

680
01:18:20.695 --> 01:18:22.030
I also want to learn!

681
01:18:22.655 --> 01:18:23.281
Gui. why do you want

682
01:18:23.531 --> 01:18:24.949
to learn martial arts?

683
01:18:25.200 --> 01:18:26.951
So the others won't bully me.

684
01:18:27.619 --> 01:18:28.661
What about you?

685
01:18:28.661 --> 01:18:30.121
I want everyone to be afraid of me.

686
01:18:30.663 --> 01:18:32.248
What if Ning bullies you. what will you do?

687
01:18:32.498 --> 01:18:33.833
I will hit him back

688
01:18:34.792 --> 01:18:36.669
What about you. will you fight Gui back?

689
01:18:36.669 --> 01:18:38.630
For sure.
I will fight Gui until he's scared of me.

690
01:18:38.880 --> 01:18:39.756
What if you can't beat him?

691
01:18:40.006 --> 01:18:41.674
Then. I will learn from a master

692
01:18:42.675 --> 01:18:43.843
Then what will you do?

693
01:18:43.843 --> 01:18:46.012
I will learn from a master

694
01:18:46.262 --> 01:18:47.889
and then fight him again.

695
01:18:49.682 --> 01:18:51.809
You beat him up. and he beats you up.

696
01:18:51.809 --> 01:18:54.062
When will this end?

697
01:18:59.192 --> 01:19:01.569
It's not that I don't want to teach you.

698
01:19:02.862 --> 01:19:04.781
I also need to think about

699
01:19:05.031 --> 01:19:06.616
why we learn martial arts.

700
01:19:08.368 --> 01:19:11.079
Let's go and catch the dragonflies!

701
01:19:59.460 --> 01:20:00.003
Grandma. let's eat.

702
01:20:00.253 --> 01:20:01.671
Ok.

703
01:20:08.428 --> 01:20:09.512
Grandma

704
01:20:09.762 --> 01:20:12.265
- Moon... - Yes. Grandma.

705
01:20:13.266 --> 01:20:15.810
In a few days.

706
01:20:16.227 --> 01:20:19.981
we should visit your parents' graves.

707
01:20:20.481 --> 01:20:21.441
Ok.

708
01:20:29.782 --> 01:20:30.825
I am going to...

709
01:20:30.825 --> 01:20:32.785
visit my parents' graves.

710
01:20:45.298 --> 01:20:46.591
Hey. Ox.

711
01:21:57.662 --> 01:21:58.663
Have a drink of water.

712
01:22:05.878 --> 01:22:07.505
Can we talk?

713
01:22:10.341 --> 01:22:11.426
You are leaving...

714
01:22:16.889 --> 01:22:18.349
I was thinking...

715
01:22:18.850 --> 01:22:20.476
maybe I should visit my parents' graves.

716
01:22:22.520 --> 01:22:24.897
You should go. Family is important.

717
01:23:11.360 --> 01:23:12.945
I'll come back soon.

718
01:23:18.951 --> 01:23:20.578
You've been here for many years.

719
01:23:21.120 --> 01:23:24.916
Yet I've always known one day you will leave.

720
01:23:25.958 --> 01:23:27.210
The truth is. I...

721
01:23:38.012 --> 01:23:41.766
Take these clean clothes for your trip.

722
01:23:46.312 --> 01:23:48.314
You don't even know my real name.

723
01:23:50.525 --> 01:23:51.901
You don't have to tell me.

724
01:23:52.735 --> 01:23:55.321
I don't need to know where you're from...

725
01:23:55.988 --> 01:23:57.406
or where you're going.

726
01:23:58.616 --> 01:24:00.618
You will always be "Ox" to me.

727
01:24:06.707 --> 01:24:08.501
My name is Huo Yuanjia.

728
01:24:50.668 --> 01:24:52.044
I'll always remember.

729
01:26:24.178 --> 01:26:27.932
Late Qing Dynasty

730
01:26:28.516 --> 01:26:32.019
Various strong countries invaded China

731
01:26:33.145 --> 01:26:36.565
Tianjin became partly colonised

732
01:27:02.216 --> 01:27:03.259
Believe in God. and you'll have everlasting life.

733
01:27:03.509 --> 01:27:06.220
...his words are written here.

734
01:27:06.220 --> 01:27:08.139
God's words...

735
01:27:35.291 --> 01:27:36.500
Huo Yuanjia!

736
01:27:37.251 --> 01:27:39.587
Champion of Tianjin!

737
01:27:39.837 --> 01:27:41.255
Huo Yuanjia!

738
01:27:42.381 --> 01:27:45.259
Champion of Tianjin! Huo Yuanjia!

739
01:27:47.261 --> 01:27:50.014
Huo Yuanjia has returned to the ring.

740
01:27:52.224 --> 01:27:54.560
Huo Yuanjia has returned to the ring.

741
01:28:39.897 --> 01:28:41.690
- Young master! - Lai!

742
01:28:41.941 --> 01:28:43.025
You've finally returned!

743
01:28:43.275 --> 01:28:44.318
Good. good...

744
01:28:44.318 --> 01:28:45.486
Let me take your bag.

745
01:29:17.101 --> 01:29:20.020
Please forgive me...

746
01:29:20.354 --> 01:29:22.857
it was not easy maintaining this house.

747
01:29:45.546 --> 01:29:49.383
I did my best...

748
01:29:50.050 --> 01:29:51.427
trying to keep everything...

749
01:29:51.427 --> 01:29:53.137
the way it was.

750
01:29:55.764 --> 01:29:57.308
It must have been very hard for you.

751
01:29:57.975 --> 01:29:59.518
I'm sorry for not doing better.

752
01:30:00.102 --> 01:30:01.395
Young Master.

753
01:30:01.395 --> 01:30:02.688
After you left...

754
01:30:03.147 --> 01:30:06.025
the creditors came... to collect money.

755
01:30:06.400 --> 01:30:07.902
tearing this place...

756
01:30:08.402 --> 01:30:10.905
apart.

757
01:30:11.405 --> 01:30:15.326
The house was almost foreclosed.

758
01:30:17.328 --> 01:30:19.663
We would have lost...

759
01:30:19.997 --> 01:30:21.540
everything...

760
01:30:22.082 --> 01:30:25.336
but someone sent money.

761
01:30:26.420 --> 01:30:28.213
I later figured...

762
01:30:28.547 --> 01:30:32.593
it was your good friend Mr. Nong Jinsun.

763
01:30:46.649 --> 01:30:48.400
I don't need these anymore.

764
01:30:50.945 --> 01:30:51.904
Neither do...

765
01:30:52.154 --> 01:30:53.781
my parents.

766
01:30:57.368 --> 01:30:58.452
Father...

767
01:30:59.870 --> 01:31:01.455
I...

768
01:31:02.373 --> 01:31:05.292
finally realised...

769
01:31:05.709 --> 01:31:08.462
why you held back the last blow.

770
01:31:09.797 --> 01:31:13.092
You are the true Champion.

771
01:31:14.468 --> 01:31:15.844
Mother.

772
01:31:16.470 --> 01:31:19.306
you taught me how to be a good person.

773
01:31:20.808 --> 01:31:23.477
I was too arrogant to understand.

774
01:31:27.272 --> 01:31:28.232
Rest assured

775
01:31:28.482 --> 01:31:31.193
I will not disappoint you again.

776
01:31:38.117 --> 01:31:39.201
My dear Jade.

777
01:31:40.494 --> 01:31:43.539
I was not a good father.

778
01:31:45.290 --> 01:31:47.501
And because of me. you suffered a horrible death.

779
01:31:50.754 --> 01:31:52.798
I was never good enough for you.

780
01:32:29.001 --> 01:32:30.210
Let's have tea.

781
01:32:47.895 --> 01:32:49.730
Sir. I am sorry.

782
01:32:49.730 --> 01:32:51.065
My boss does not want to see you.

783
01:32:51.315 --> 01:32:52.983
but he wants you to have this.

784
01:33:18.258 --> 01:33:21.345
Watch your way.

785
01:33:23.222 --> 01:33:26.183
Leave a way. Excuse me...

786
01:33:47.621 --> 01:33:51.625
Mrs. Chin. I am very sorry for what I have done.

787
01:33:52.584 --> 01:33:55.587
Please allow me to pay my respects.

788
01:34:13.105 --> 01:34:15.399
Mother. Mother.

789
01:34:42.467 --> 01:34:43.927
Get out and kneel down.

790
01:34:47.139 --> 01:34:49.141
You'll gonna have a hard time if you come again

791
01:34:49.391 --> 01:34:50.309
You dare to come with no money?

792
01:34:50.559 --> 01:34:51.143
Get away?

793
01:34:51.393 --> 01:34:52.394
Don't come again or you'll have a hard time.

794
01:34:52.644 --> 01:34:54.563
Get away...

795
01:35:00.694 --> 01:35:01.612
Master...

796
01:35:02.779 --> 01:35:03.655
Master...

797
01:35:03.906 --> 01:35:04.698
Master...

798
01:35:04.698 --> 01:35:06.366
- Master. we are sorry! - we are sorry!

799
01:35:08.202 --> 01:35:09.703
Master. I learned kung fu
with you since I was a child.

800
01:35:10.204 --> 01:35:13.040
I don't know another

801
01:35:13.373 --> 01:35:15.918
way to making a living.

802
01:35:16.668 --> 01:35:18.921
Now you are back. and...

803
01:35:20.297 --> 01:35:21.715
Master. please forgive us!

804
01:35:22.716 --> 01:35:23.717
Stand up...

805
01:35:33.352 --> 01:35:37.522
Fresh pork. reasonable price!

806
01:35:41.902 --> 01:35:42.903
Fresh pork...

807
01:35:42.903 --> 01:35:45.739
Madam.

808
01:35:45.739 --> 01:35:48.158
Come here. madam... It's great for making soup.

809
01:35:48.408 --> 01:35:50.285
it is really cheap today.

810
01:35:53.622 --> 01:35:54.748
Two catty (or One Kilogram) of pork please!

811
01:35:58.585 --> 01:35:59.711
No business with you!

812
01:36:26.655 --> 01:36:27.781
Extra release!

813
01:36:27.781 --> 01:36:30.867
Hercules O'Brien...

814
01:36:31.118 --> 01:36:32.786
32 plays without losing one

815
01:36:32.786 --> 01:36:35.330
23 fighters seriously injured.

816
01:36:35.580 --> 01:36:37.499
challenges all Chinese fighters.

817
01:36:37.791 --> 01:36:38.959
Vows to defeat every...

818
01:36:39.209 --> 01:36:40.794
"Sick Man of Asia."

819
01:36:41.044 --> 01:36:43.005
No one dare to challenge him.

820
01:36:46.508 --> 01:36:47.718
Jinsun.

821
01:36:50.345 --> 01:36:51.722
I'm so sorry for what I've done.

822
01:36:52.806 --> 01:36:54.975
I realised my mistakes...

823
01:36:56.268 --> 01:36:57.686
only too late!

824
01:36:59.062 --> 01:37:00.814
It hurts to think about it.

825
01:37:02.774 --> 01:37:04.484
Let's forget about the past.

826
01:37:05.444 --> 01:37:06.862
That chapter is over.

827
01:37:14.244 --> 01:37:15.537
Jinsun...

828
01:37:15.829 --> 01:37:17.331
I don't know how to begin.

829
01:37:17.581 --> 01:37:19.041
but you're the only one I can turn to.

830
01:37:19.833 --> 01:37:21.543
I need to borrow some money.

831
01:37:21.835 --> 01:37:23.837
What? You still want to fight?

832
01:37:24.838 --> 01:37:26.048
Yes.

833
01:37:27.799 --> 01:37:29.593
You cannot go down that path again.

834
01:37:30.093 --> 01:37:31.928
I will not give you any money.

835
01:38:20.894 --> 01:38:21.895
Young Master.

836
01:38:22.771 --> 01:38:23.897
Master Huo.

837
01:38:23.897 --> 01:38:25.941
my master wants you to have this.

838
01:38:30.195 --> 01:38:31.696
Who's your master?

839
01:38:31.947 --> 01:38:34.825
His name is Nong. Nong Jinsun.

840
01:38:40.414 --> 01:38:43.417
The Shanghai Race Club 1909

841
01:38:56.054 --> 01:38:58.223
Ladies and Gentlemen...

842
01:38:58.723 --> 01:39:02.227
Brace yourself... for a man who

843
01:39:02.644 --> 01:39:05.564
can move a train with one hand...

844
01:39:05.939 --> 01:39:08.650
and punch through the Great Wall.

845
01:39:09.651 --> 01:39:11.069
He can kill a Chinese fighter...

846
01:39:11.319 --> 01:39:14.281
with his little finger.

847
01:39:15.657 --> 01:39:17.117
Now. Welcome the 9th Wonder of the world...

848
01:39:17.117 --> 01:39:20.036
the strongest man in history...

849
01:39:20.036 --> 01:39:22.789
O'Brien!

850
01:39:47.731 --> 01:39:49.733
Today's challenger is...

851
01:39:50.275 --> 01:39:53.278
Huo Yuanjia of Tianjin!

852
01:39:58.033 --> 01:40:00.577
Good!

853
01:40:16.092 --> 01:40:17.802
Sign the Death Waiver.

854
01:40:19.429 --> 01:40:20.555
Please inform him.

855
01:40:21.097 --> 01:40:23.266
that taking a life in a competition...

856
01:40:23.517 --> 01:40:25.185
is a cruel and backward tradition.

857
01:40:25.769 --> 01:40:27.646
May I suggest that we compete

858
01:40:27.896 --> 01:40:29.272
with honour and civility.

859
01:40:39.449 --> 01:40:41.910
He wants to kick your butt.

860
01:40:47.707 --> 01:40:48.166
Come On

861
01:40:48.416 --> 01:40:50.377
Let the match begin!

862
01:41:01.179 --> 01:41:02.222
Come On

863
01:41:07.769 --> 01:41:08.812
Come On

864
01:41:33.086 --> 01:41:34.087
Good!

865
01:43:46.594 --> 01:43:49.222
Good! Good!

866
01:43:54.978 --> 01:43:56.229
It's an honour.

867
01:44:26.843 --> 01:44:28.178
Thank you.

868
01:44:32.056 --> 01:44:34.267
Good!

869
01:44:44.861 --> 01:44:46.738
Chinese Martial Artist Defeats US Champion O'Brien

870
01:44:46.988 --> 01:44:49.783
Chinese Fighter Defeats Western Boxer.

871
01:44:50.033 --> 01:44:51.409
Victory Shocks Shanghai!

872
01:44:51.409 --> 01:44:55.538
Huo Yuanjia Says Wushu Schools Must Unite

873
01:44:56.581 --> 01:44:58.291
Fighter Founds Jingwu Sports Federation.

874
01:44:58.541 --> 01:44:59.667
Recruits Country's Best

875
01:45:01.294 --> 01:45:04.214
Shanghai Foreign Correspondents Club

876
01:45:06.299 --> 01:45:07.300
Thank you.

877
01:45:08.176 --> 01:45:09.052
Master!

878
01:45:09.302 --> 01:45:10.804
You've received a dinner invitation.

879
01:45:20.897 --> 01:45:22.482
I never dreamed it would be you.

880
01:45:23.149 --> 01:45:26.569
I've been waiting for this day. Yuanjia.

881
01:45:29.113 --> 01:45:30.365
Am I still your friend?

882
01:45:31.324 --> 01:45:33.201
Your friendship... is very important to me.

883
01:45:34.077 --> 01:45:35.328
How can I not?

884
01:45:35.912 --> 01:45:39.457
I always knew that you would not disappoint me.

885
01:45:41.751 --> 01:45:43.753
But I did. for a long time.

886
01:45:45.213 --> 01:45:47.799
Let's not talk about the past.

887
01:45:48.550 --> 01:45:50.385
Come. have a seat.

888
01:45:52.428 --> 01:45:54.722
Here. your favourite wine.

889
01:45:56.474 --> 01:45:57.350
Come on.

890
01:45:59.310 --> 01:46:00.353
What's the matter?

891
01:46:00.353 --> 01:46:02.772
I stopped drinking. A long time ago.

892
01:46:03.356 --> 01:46:05.400
Why?

893
01:46:05.692 --> 01:46:07.694
But you loved to drink.

894
01:46:08.111 --> 01:46:10.363
I've learned from my mistakes.

895
01:46:12.782 --> 01:46:13.992
That's wonderful.

896
01:46:14.659 --> 01:46:17.328
Let's have tea instead.

897
01:46:26.337 --> 01:46:27.380
Yuanjia.

898
01:46:28.756 --> 01:46:32.677
Your victory gained respect
for all Chinese people.

899
01:46:33.386 --> 01:46:35.430
The foreigners have bullied us for too long.

900
01:46:35.972 --> 01:46:37.849
Someone should stand up.

901
01:46:38.391 --> 01:46:40.101
If that hadn't happened.
they would have continued to see us

902
01:46:40.351 --> 01:46:41.811
as the sick man of East Asia!

903
01:46:42.770 --> 01:46:43.938
My friend...

904
01:46:44.689 --> 01:46:46.232
I'm really proud of you.

905
01:46:46.941 --> 01:46:48.067
Enjoy!

906
01:46:50.945 --> 01:46:52.405
Chinese must get strengthened.

907
01:46:53.406 --> 01:46:54.991
The Westerners despised us partially

908
01:46:55.617 --> 01:46:57.493
because we've been busy

909
01:46:57.493 --> 01:46:59.871
fighting among ourselves.

910
01:47:00.705 --> 01:47:03.750
That becomes a laughing stock for others.

911
01:47:07.337 --> 01:47:09.881
Foreigners see us as the sick man of East Asia!

912
01:47:10.423 --> 01:47:11.883
What they call us is irrelevant.

913
01:47:12.717 --> 01:47:13.468
What matters is

914
01:47:13.468 --> 01:47:16.554
if we are really sick.

915
01:47:18.765 --> 01:47:20.850
or. if we are not attempting to cure

916
01:47:21.100 --> 01:47:22.560
the disease even

917
01:47:22.560 --> 01:47:24.354
when we know it is there.

918
01:47:25.146 --> 01:47:27.023
They still flaunt their superiority.

919
01:47:33.446 --> 01:47:37.784
I didn't expect you to be so insightful.

920
01:47:39.327 --> 01:47:44.791
Compared to you. I am kind of bookish.

921
01:47:53.049 --> 01:47:54.092
Jinsun.

922
01:47:54.425 --> 01:47:55.635
when do you return to Tianjin?

923
01:47:56.386 --> 01:47:58.763
I'm going to stay in Shanghai.

924
01:48:00.098 --> 01:48:01.683
Who about your restaurant?

925
01:48:03.476 --> 01:48:04.227
I sold it.

926
01:48:04.477 --> 01:48:05.561
What?

927
01:48:06.145 --> 01:48:07.647
But it was so profitable.

928
01:48:08.272 --> 01:48:10.191
The Jingwu Sports Federation needs...

929
01:48:10.525 --> 01:48:12.485
start-up funds.

930
01:48:15.446 --> 01:48:18.658
But the restaurant has been your life!

931
01:48:19.492 --> 01:48:20.994
My restaurant means little...

932
01:48:21.244 --> 01:48:22.662
compared to...

933
01:48:22.662 --> 01:48:24.414
your vision.

934
01:48:25.206 --> 01:48:26.249
Yuanjia.

935
01:48:26.499 --> 01:48:28.334
I do not know Wushu.

936
01:48:29.752 --> 01:48:33.506
but I do know how to help.

937
01:48:35.466 --> 01:48:36.551
I hope it will enough.

938
01:48:39.303 --> 01:48:40.388
Jinsun!

939
01:48:41.014 --> 01:48:42.932
I was gone for quite a few years.

940
01:48:43.850 --> 01:48:46.519
Everyday I asked myself

941
01:48:46.894 --> 01:48:49.522
why I learned kung fu.

942
01:48:50.148 --> 01:48:53.735
and whether or not it was only for fighting.

943
01:48:54.610 --> 01:48:56.195
Have you had an answer?

944
01:48:58.656 --> 01:49:00.033
Only the weak

945
01:49:00.700 --> 01:49:03.619
need to prove their power through force.

946
01:49:05.621 --> 01:49:08.541
but what force leads to

947
01:49:08.541 --> 01:49:10.251
is endless hatred.

948
01:49:11.544 --> 01:49:12.962
I want to change kung fu

949
01:49:13.212 --> 01:49:15.506
into a sport.

950
01:49:16.549 --> 01:49:19.802
with which one can shape oneself
both physically and spiritually.

951
01:49:20.136 --> 01:49:21.387
That's a good idea.

952
01:49:22.388 --> 01:49:24.432
You should let more know about it.

953
01:49:26.225 --> 01:49:28.686
I don't know how much I can achieve.

954
01:49:29.937 --> 01:49:31.564
but I will try my best.

955
01:49:36.611 --> 01:49:37.904
Did you hear that?

956
01:49:38.821 --> 01:49:39.906
Yes.

957
01:49:41.199 --> 01:49:44.327
I heard a voice calling.

958
01:49:46.579 --> 01:49:48.206
Now what we hear

959
01:49:48.456 --> 01:49:49.999
is the same voice!

960
01:49:53.586 --> 01:49:56.714
Jingwu Sports Federation

961
01:50:00.593 --> 01:50:01.594
Yuanjia!

962
01:50:03.346 --> 01:50:03.971
Zhaojian

963
01:50:04.222 --> 01:50:05.223
I was wrong to disrespect you.

964
01:50:06.057 --> 01:50:07.600
Master Huo. I hope that...

965
01:50:08.351 --> 01:50:09.143
I am so glad that you are here.

966
01:50:09.393 --> 01:50:10.770
I was going to pick you up.

967
01:50:11.604 --> 01:50:12.605
Laifu.

968
01:50:12.605 --> 01:50:13.356
Master

969
01:50:13.606 --> 01:50:15.108
would you please show Mr. Zhao around?

970
01:50:19.278 --> 01:50:20.238
Yuanjia!

971
01:50:22.615 --> 01:50:25.243
As we've discussed. the Jingwu Manifesto.

972
01:50:25.493 --> 01:50:26.577
Take a look.

973
01:50:29.622 --> 01:50:32.458
Our motto:

974
01:50:32.959 --> 01:50:35.628
"Body. Mind and Soul".

975
01:50:36.879 --> 01:50:39.632
Wushu is a way to cultivate one's body.
mind and soul.

976
01:50:39.966 --> 01:50:41.467
All Wushu disciplines are respected equally.

977
01:50:41.759 --> 01:50:44.345
By working together...

978
01:50:46.222 --> 01:50:49.016
We can better ourselves...

979
01:50:49.517 --> 01:50:52.145
and stand strong as one nation

980
01:50:52.436 --> 01:50:55.857
We influence others through...

981
01:50:56.107 --> 01:50:59.652
cooperation. not intimidation.

982
01:50:59.652 --> 01:51:00.862
Through this ideal. we will always...

983
01:51:01.112 --> 01:51:02.655
Stand Strong!

984
01:51:03.656 --> 01:51:05.867
Jingwu Sports Federation 1910

985
01:51:10.830 --> 01:51:11.914
Shanghai Foreign Chamber of Commerce

986
01:51:12.165 --> 01:51:13.708
Well. gentlemen. it's too rich for me.

987
01:51:13.958 --> 01:51:16.002
I only bet on sure things.

988
01:51:18.504 --> 01:51:19.839
Then perhaps you'll be interested...

989
01:51:19.839 --> 01:51:22.800
in joining our little wager against this...

990
01:51:22.800 --> 01:51:24.886
Huo Yuanjia fellow?

991
01:51:25.553 --> 01:51:26.679
He'd better lose this time.

992
01:51:26.929 --> 01:51:30.224
It cost me 6.000 francs
when he beat this O' Brien.

993
01:51:30.683 --> 01:51:32.185
Mr. Mita here...

994
01:51:32.435 --> 01:51:35.688
will ensure that you win back
everything that you lost...

995
01:51:35.688 --> 01:51:37.064
plus a little bit more.

996
01:51:37.398 --> 01:51:40.443
I've suggested a competition of four matches...

997
01:51:40.693 --> 01:51:42.945
between our countries' best against him.

998
01:51:43.279 --> 01:51:46.782
We beat him and leave
the Chinese with nothing to brag about.

999
01:51:47.033 --> 01:51:48.367
Four against one?

1000
01:51:48.659 --> 01:51:51.454
What makes you so sure he is going to accept that?

1001
01:51:51.704 --> 01:51:53.372
Pride? Honour?

1002
01:51:53.623 --> 01:51:55.166
The prestige of his school?

1003
01:51:55.416 --> 01:51:56.709
It's of no importance.

1004
01:51:57.084 --> 01:51:59.086
He has already accepted the challenge.

1005
01:51:59.503 --> 01:52:01.964
Then. gentlemen. I'll take you up on your wager.

1006
01:52:02.215 --> 01:52:04.008
And to make it a little more interesting...

1007
01:52:04.717 --> 01:52:06.719
I'm going to back the Chinese.

1008
01:52:08.095 --> 01:52:11.390
Mita... you are certain Huo Yuanjia will lose?

1009
01:52:11.641 --> 01:52:13.559
With what I have in mind...

1010
01:52:13.893 --> 01:52:15.811
our victory is guaranteed.

1011
01:52:35.623 --> 01:52:36.499
Yuanjia

1012
01:52:38.376 --> 01:52:39.752
One of the contestants

1013
01:52:39.752 --> 01:52:42.380
Tanaka. the Japanese fighter...

1014
01:52:42.630 --> 01:52:43.839
wishes to meet you.

1015
01:52:44.298 --> 01:52:47.760
I heard he remains undefeated.
He is one of the best.

1016
01:52:50.763 --> 01:52:53.015
Good. one can always learn from the best.

1017
01:52:53.766 --> 01:52:56.894
I suspect that the Foreign Chamber of Commerce...

1018
01:52:57.144 --> 01:52:58.896
might have a hidden agenda.

1019
01:52:58.896 --> 01:52:59.814
How can they set up...

1020
01:52:59.814 --> 01:53:02.400
a 'one against four' contest?

1021
01:53:02.817 --> 01:53:03.859
It is...

1022
01:53:04.110 --> 01:53:06.821
an attempt to humiliate us.

1023
01:53:07.071 --> 01:53:10.533
and undermine our position.

1024
01:53:11.784 --> 01:53:12.868
You're right.

1025
01:53:13.703 --> 01:53:16.497
One against four is unfair...

1026
01:53:16.789 --> 01:53:18.207
plus I have to win each match.

1027
01:53:20.293 --> 01:53:21.836
But not everything in life...

1028
01:53:22.795 --> 01:53:25.798
is fair.

1029
01:53:28.801 --> 01:53:30.469
For the sake of the Federation.

1030
01:53:32.513 --> 01:53:33.806
I have no other choice.

1031
01:53:34.348 --> 01:53:35.683
What if?

1032
01:53:36.809 --> 01:53:40.229
Jinsun. I want to ask you to do something...

1033
01:53:40.479 --> 01:53:41.480
What is it?

1034
01:53:42.815 --> 01:53:45.818
After this fight.
you should head the Sports Federation.

1035
01:53:46.527 --> 01:53:47.570
Why?

1036
01:53:49.697 --> 01:53:52.825
I want to visit Moon and Grandma.

1037
01:53:53.284 --> 01:53:54.535
I made a promise.

1038
01:54:08.632 --> 01:54:10.217
Do you know anything...

1039
01:54:10.843 --> 01:54:12.928
about teas?

1040
01:54:14.847 --> 01:54:17.725
I don't really want to know...

1041
01:54:18.642 --> 01:54:21.145
because I don't like categories.

1042
01:54:21.562 --> 01:54:22.855
Tea is tea.

1043
01:54:22.855 --> 01:54:24.940
Each has its own characteristics

1044
01:54:24.940 --> 01:54:26.609
hence different grades.

1045
01:54:29.403 --> 01:54:31.989
What's the purpose of grading?

1046
01:54:33.366 --> 01:54:36.035
All teas are grown in nature...

1047
01:54:36.619 --> 01:54:37.912
with little discernible differences

1048
01:54:38.704 --> 01:54:39.997
So you really don't know teas.

1049
01:54:40.748 --> 01:54:42.875
Once you learn you can tell the differences.

1050
01:54:43.667 --> 01:54:45.044
Maybe you're right.

1051
01:54:45.419 --> 01:54:47.296
The way I see it...

1052
01:54:47.588 --> 01:54:49.382
the tea does not...

1053
01:54:49.632 --> 01:54:51.801
judge itself.

1054
01:54:52.051 --> 01:54:54.011
People...

1055
01:54:54.303 --> 01:54:56.263
judge the tea.

1056
01:54:56.931 --> 01:54:58.933
As for me. I don't want to do that.

1057
01:54:59.183 --> 01:55:01.477
Why not?

1058
01:55:01.936 --> 01:55:04.021
When you are in a good mood.

1059
01:55:04.313 --> 01:55:05.898
the grade of the tea...

1060
01:55:06.899 --> 01:55:09.402
does not matter.

1061
01:55:09.902 --> 01:55:12.405
I've never seen it that way.

1062
01:55:12.655 --> 01:55:16.409
In your opinion. is one style of Wushu superior...

1063
01:55:16.992 --> 01:55:20.746
to another?

1064
01:55:21.038 --> 01:55:22.498
I don't think so.

1065
01:55:23.916 --> 01:55:26.877
If no particular style is superior...

1066
01:55:27.795 --> 01:55:29.797
why have...

1067
01:55:30.381 --> 01:55:32.133
so many competitions?

1068
01:55:32.758 --> 01:55:35.010
I believe...

1069
01:55:35.010 --> 01:55:37.388
no single style is superior.

1070
01:55:37.847 --> 01:55:40.433
Only different skill levels.

1071
01:55:41.267 --> 01:55:42.935
It is through training that...

1072
01:55:42.935 --> 01:55:44.937
one discovers one's strength.

1073
01:55:45.938 --> 01:55:47.940
Perhaps. the most formidable...

1074
01:55:48.315 --> 01:55:49.900
enemy lies within oneself.

1075
01:55:50.401 --> 01:55:54.155
Competitions can lead us
to a path of self-discovery?

1076
01:55:54.864 --> 01:55:55.948
You mean...

1077
01:55:55.948 --> 01:55:56.907
our most important battle...

1078
01:55:57.158 --> 01:55:58.701
is actually fought within?

1079
01:56:09.503 --> 01:56:11.088
Your words

1080
01:56:11.088 --> 01:56:14.008
are poignant.

1081
01:56:16.927 --> 01:56:18.929
Let's...

1082
01:56:19.180 --> 01:56:22.016
enjoy the tea.

1083
01:56:22.516 --> 01:56:25.644
- Please enjoy. - Thank you.

1084
01:57:54.024 --> 01:57:58.070
Shanghai 1910

1085
01:58:00.489 --> 01:58:03.826
French Concession Pierre Theatre

1086
01:58:06.120 --> 01:58:08.122
The Fight Arena

1087
01:58:39.903 --> 01:58:42.406
Today's battle

1088
01:58:42.656 --> 01:58:45.492
is between four fighters
from the Foreign Chamber of Commerce

1089
01:58:45.743 --> 01:58:48.829
and Huo Yuanjia of the Jingwu Sports Federation.

1090
01:58:58.797 --> 01:59:00.549
Whichever side falls first

1091
01:59:00.799 --> 01:59:02.426
or signals to admit defeat

1092
01:59:02.676 --> 01:59:05.846
will be considered to have lost the match.

1093
01:59:07.556 --> 01:59:09.141
This is unusual.

1094
01:59:10.893 --> 01:59:12.686
Four against one?

1095
01:59:14.229 --> 01:59:16.231
You never told me.

1096
01:59:16.231 --> 01:59:17.775
Both the Chamber of Commerce...

1097
01:59:18.025 --> 01:59:20.152
and the Federation agreed.

1098
01:59:20.152 --> 01:59:21.362
Don't be concerned.

1099
01:59:21.654 --> 01:59:23.906
This is not a competition.

1100
01:59:25.199 --> 01:59:26.617
This is murder.

1101
01:59:26.867 --> 01:59:29.036
Tanaka. you're overreacting.

1102
01:59:29.411 --> 01:59:31.664
Huo Yuanjia fought the best fighters...
from around the world.

1103
01:59:31.914 --> 01:59:33.165
and won each time.

1104
01:59:33.165 --> 01:59:35.459
The rules -- he set them up.

1105
01:59:35.709 --> 01:59:37.169
Mita.

1106
01:59:38.879 --> 01:59:40.506
What's your deal?

1107
01:59:41.590 --> 01:59:43.342
Is this really for the pride of Japan?

1108
01:59:43.592 --> 01:59:45.177
Or did you place a large bet?

1109
01:59:47.179 --> 01:59:48.597
The spirit of Wushu...

1110
01:59:49.181 --> 01:59:50.808
is the most important thing.

1111
01:59:54.186 --> 01:59:55.938
To compete is to win.

1112
01:59:56.689 --> 01:59:59.483
Now the first round!
Huo Yuanjia against the British boxer!

1113
02:00:03.821 --> 02:00:06.532
British Boxer. Peter Smith

1114
02:00:11.537 --> 02:00:12.204
Start!

1115
02:00:47.531 --> 02:00:50.659
Belgium Royal Riding Coach. Hanks Herzog

1116
02:01:46.298 --> 02:01:47.299
Great job. master!

1117
02:01:57.017 --> 02:02:00.187
Fencing champion of Europe. Antony Kasia

1118
02:03:07.337 --> 02:03:09.381
This is our embarrassment. We can't let him win.

1119
02:03:19.600 --> 02:03:21.560
The fourth and final contest will now begin.

1120
02:03:21.560 --> 02:03:24.563
The competitor to represent
the Foreign Chamber of Commerce...

1121
02:03:24.563 --> 02:03:27.441
is Tanaka from Japan.

1122
02:03:31.153 --> 02:03:31.987
Begin!

1123
02:03:32.654 --> 02:03:33.947
Yuanjia.

1124
02:03:34.406 --> 02:03:36.950
This is an unfair contest.

1125
02:03:37.659 --> 02:03:40.621
If you wish to re-schedule...

1126
02:03:40.954 --> 02:03:42.915
that's fine with me.

1127
02:03:43.498 --> 02:03:45.375
You're very kind.

1128
02:03:45.918 --> 02:03:47.836
We started the fight...

1129
02:03:48.420 --> 02:03:49.796
we must finish.

1130
02:03:50.964 --> 02:03:51.757
Please!

1131
02:04:09.816 --> 02:04:10.484
Begin!

1132
02:05:20.345 --> 02:05:21.430
Master. that's great!

1133
02:06:08.560 --> 02:06:10.353
This round is a draw.

1134
02:06:10.812 --> 02:06:13.023
Please set down your weapons. gentlemen...

1135
02:06:13.565 --> 02:06:15.317
and prepare for hand-to-hand combat.

1136
02:06:18.904 --> 02:06:20.739
Mita. where have you been?

1137
02:06:20.739 --> 02:06:22.282
This is embarrassing. He's going to lose.

1138
02:06:23.325 --> 02:06:25.827
Don't worry. gentlemen. I have it under control.

1139
02:07:20.966 --> 02:07:21.716
Yuanjia!

1140
02:07:34.813 --> 02:07:35.939
Time out!

1141
02:07:36.648 --> 02:07:39.651
- What's going on? - What is he doing?

1142
02:07:43.822 --> 02:07:44.364
Yuanjia!

1143
02:07:44.614 --> 02:07:47.075
- Tanaka! - Go now! Go! Go!

1144
02:07:52.205 --> 02:07:53.832
What happened? What happened?

1145
02:07:54.916 --> 02:07:55.750
What happened?

1146
02:07:56.001 --> 02:07:56.918
Poisoned!

1147
02:07:57.169 --> 02:08:00.005
Poison? What poison?

1148
02:08:00.463 --> 02:08:01.673
How did this happen?

1149
02:08:02.966 --> 02:08:04.676
- What do you need? - Tea...

1150
02:08:04.676 --> 02:08:05.969
Tea!

1151
02:08:06.386 --> 02:08:07.554
Where's the teapot?

1152
02:08:08.221 --> 02:08:11.725
The tea is laced. But it's gone!

1153
02:08:11.725 --> 02:08:14.269
We're going straight to the hospital.

1154
02:08:15.687 --> 02:08:19.441
Too late. The toxin is...

1155
02:08:19.691 --> 02:08:20.317
in my blood!

1156
02:08:20.567 --> 02:08:22.485
Let me take revenge.

1157
02:08:25.322 --> 02:08:26.615
Sheng.

1158
02:08:28.700 --> 02:08:30.243
We...

1159
02:08:30.952 --> 02:08:32.370
must not.

1160
02:08:35.582 --> 02:08:36.708
Revenge only...

1161
02:08:37.584 --> 02:08:39.711
brings more bloodshed.

1162
02:08:41.379 --> 02:08:42.923
No more revenge.

1163
02:08:45.717 --> 02:08:48.970
We must strive to better ourselves.

1164
02:08:49.221 --> 02:08:52.474
Forget the competition.

1165
02:08:52.724 --> 02:08:54.768
We're going to hospital.

1166
02:08:58.521 --> 02:08:59.731
Jinsun.

1167
02:09:00.941 --> 02:09:02.984
It took me years to understand...

1168
02:09:04.819 --> 02:09:08.740
the true meaning of Wushu.

1169
02:09:10.492 --> 02:09:12.577
and its purpose.

1170
02:09:13.787 --> 02:09:15.747
The competition must continue.

1171
02:09:17.040 --> 02:09:18.833
One cannot choose...

1172
02:09:18.833 --> 02:09:20.752
how one's life begins.

1173
02:09:23.088 --> 02:09:26.758
But one can choose...
to face the end with courage.

1174
02:09:32.639 --> 02:09:33.765
Master.

1175
02:09:34.307 --> 02:09:36.810
What are you doing?
Finish him off in the next round!

1176
02:09:36.810 --> 02:09:38.019
Why do you say that?

1177
02:09:38.937 --> 02:09:40.272
It's not for you to decide.

1178
02:09:40.522 --> 02:09:41.856
I must win this fight!

1179
02:09:41.856 --> 02:09:43.775
Whatever it takes. Just win!

1180
02:09:52.534 --> 02:09:54.202
We... Stand strong!

1181
02:09:54.452 --> 02:10:04.004
Stand strong! Stand strong!

1182
02:10:04.254 --> 02:10:05.338
You really want to win?

1183
02:10:26.443 --> 02:10:27.610
Let's stop.

1184
02:10:28.069 --> 02:10:30.822
Treasure your life.

1185
02:10:33.283 --> 02:10:34.284
Listen to them...

1186
02:10:35.827 --> 02:10:37.829
it's not just about me.

1187
02:10:43.835 --> 02:10:44.836
If you wish to continue.

1188
02:10:45.420 --> 02:10:47.964
I won't hold back.

1189
02:10:50.216 --> 02:10:51.676
It is my honour.

1190
02:12:54.257 --> 02:12:55.967
Young Master...

1191
02:12:57.385 --> 02:12:59.345
He's down! He's down! Huo Yuanjia's down!

1192
02:12:59.637 --> 02:13:02.974
Go! Go! Go!

1193
02:13:02.974 --> 02:13:04.476
Make the announcement!

1194
02:13:11.024 --> 02:13:12.609
Wait!

1195
02:13:35.173 --> 02:13:36.174
Huo...

1196
02:13:36.674 --> 02:13:39.135
Yuan... Jia!

1197
02:13:39.135 --> 02:13:41.012
Yuanjia!

1198
02:13:41.012 --> 02:13:54.442
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!

1199
02:14:01.908 --> 02:14:03.159
Tanaka. you son-of-a bitch.

1200
02:14:03.159 --> 02:14:05.036
What is this?

1201
02:14:05.036 --> 02:14:06.037
I lost!

1202
02:14:06.037 --> 02:14:08.122
Who said you lost?

1203
02:14:08.122 --> 02:14:09.999
I know it in my heart.

1204
02:14:10.250 --> 02:14:11.376
I lost. Fair and square.

1205
02:14:12.043 --> 02:14:13.253
Who do you think you are?

1206
02:14:13.503 --> 02:14:14.796
You have no right to decide.

1207
02:14:15.046 --> 02:14:17.048
You can't be Japanese.

1208
02:14:26.057 --> 02:14:29.727
You are a disgrace to Japan!

1209
02:14:31.604 --> 02:14:41.322
Huo Yuanjia! Huo Yuanjia!

1210
02:16:35.853 --> 02:16:40.733
Huo Yuanjia died from poisoning at the age of 42.

1211
02:16:42.193 --> 02:16:44.195
"The spirit of Wushu" as espoused
by Huo Yuanjia continues to

1212
02:16:44.195 --> 02:16:46.197
spread and thrive long after he passed away...

1213
02:16:46.197 --> 02:16:48.282
today. the Jingwu Sports
Federation flourishes around the world.

1214
02:16:48.533 --> 02:16:49.575
with branches in over 50 countries.

1215
02:16:50.785 --> 02:16:52.578
To commemorate Huo Yuanjia's spirit.

1216
02:16:52.829 --> 02:16:54.205
Inscribed by Sun Zhongshan. Father of the nation

1217
02:16:55.415 --> 02:16:58.459
To uphold the spirit of Wushu by Sunwen

1218
02:18:01.272 --> 02:18:02.774
Excuse me! Miss. Yang?

1219
02:18:03.191 --> 02:18:04.317
What are your chances?

1220
02:18:04.567 --> 02:18:06.569
I did my best. That's what's important.

1221
02:18:06.819 --> 02:18:08.279
Is it enough?

1221
02:18:09.305 --> 02:19:09.342
